# Firebase backend (remaining)

Skill: [`.cursor/skills/firebase-backend/SKILL.md`](../skills/firebase-backend/SKILL.md)

**Moved off Firebase:** contact, quotation, trackVisit, previewFeedback, analyticsSummary → Laravel on **`https://api.carlmanuel.com`** ([`api-carlxaeron/`](../../api-carlxaeron/), skill **api-carlxaeron**).

## Still on Firebase (`functions/index.js`)

| Export | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `assistant` | Chat agent (OpenAI) |
| `license` | Client WHMCS |
| `weeklyVisitReport` | Scheduled email report |

## `src/mapping.js`

- Forms / analytics → `api.carlmanuel.com`
- Assistant → Firebase HTTPS function

## Deploy (Firebase only)

**Gate — tests first:**

```bash
cd functions && npm test
```

Must pass before:

```bash
cd functions && npm run deploy
```

See [`.cursor/rules/test-before-deploy.mdc`](test-before-deploy.mdc).

## Email

- **Forms:** hosting API `.env` (`MAIL_*` / `SMTP_*`) — not Trigger Email
- **Weekly report:** still `functions/.env` + Trigger Email / SMTP URI as needed

## CORS (assistant)

Must include: `carlmanuel.com`, `www.carlmanuel.com`, `carlxaeron.github.io`, `localhost:3000`.

## Do not

- Commit `functions/.env` or app passwords
- Assume new form traffic writes to Firestore (historical data only)
- Redeploy legacy `contact` / `quotation` Cloud Functions as the portfolio source of truth
- Deploy functions without `npm test` passing
